question: The former leader of the National Patriotic Front of Liberia Tom Woewiyu worked with this former former President of Liberia who resigned in which year?
context:
Charles McArthur Ghankay Taylor (born 28 January 1948) is a former Liberian politician who was the 22nd President of Liberia, serving from 2 August 1997 until his resignation on 11 August 2003.

Thomas Jucontee Woewiyu is a former leader of the National Patriotic Front of Liberia.  Woewiyu served as Defense minister in the NPFL along with Charles Taylor and Ellen Johnson Sirleaf.
